# Choreographic Pipeline

This document describes a multi-agent content review workflow.
Three agents collaborate: writer, reviewer, and publisher.

# Concurrent Drafting

concurrent [(writer){draft_article} (writer){draft_summary}]

# Verification

"article draft" <- (reviewer)

# Scheduled Publication

at [[2026-04-15]] [(publisher){publish}]

# Background Monitoring

sync [(monitor){watch_metrics}]

# Time Bounded Review

until 3 days [(reviewer){final_review}]
